Name: keyg
About the game: keyg is a puzzle/arcade game with very unique gameplay. Your keyboard is a level. Each key is a room on that level. Solve puzzles, avoid enemies, discover the mystery of this strange world and befriend its inhabitants. Features Unique gameplay Big variety of puzzle and arcade levels Captivating story with numerous endings Full support of QWERTY, AZERTY and QWERTZ keyboards Colorblind mode
